title: Say Cheez
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Delivery, Take-out, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Specializes in grilled cheese sandwiches. The vegan choices, as of Oct 2014, is the build-your-own feature in which you can order vegan bread ($1.00 more) and vegan cheese ($1.50 more) and no vegan protein is available. Also has fries and onion rings; be sure to ask what kind of oil they use. Please ask staff if you can modify the regular menu items to be vegan.
